{"tid":1580290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［方向正確］網民反對丁屋申請初收成效 鄉議局擬向地政施壓","createTime":"2019-09-19T04:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T05:04:10.000Z","uid":68738,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e5053409721c9ba71ad8e279d025b00181e41248","tid":1580290,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190918/large/1568807073_2b5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568807073_2b5f.jpg&h=e7911320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗地政處10樓以往貼滿丁屋申請，現時則全部消失，告示板幾近清空。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n7.21元朗白衣人聲稱「保家衛族」，無差別襲擊市民，有網民隨即呼籲以反對丁屋申請作「清算」。據知，作為丁屋申請重地的元朗地政處，在最近1至2周，丁屋申請告示幾乎全面消失，意味近期沒有任何新申請。有消息指，鄉議局因應「清算」，欲向地政總署施壓，要求更改反對機制，包括縮短張貼期、只可由原居民提出反對，以及每宗丁屋申請只可反對一次等。<br />\n<br />\n現時地政總署收到丁屋申請後，會在分區地政處張貼申請告示14天，公眾可就申請提出反對。早前有網民在連登討論區發起，以合法途徑反對丁屋申請的行動，反對張貼在分區地政處告示板的丁屋申請，包括質疑申請人的原居民身份、懷疑申請人套丁、建屋令通道受阻或景觀受影響等。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，上述行動似有「成果」，過去一個多月，地政處接獲不少反對書，確實影響到丁屋申請程序，以往接獲最多申請的元朗區地政處，告示板經常貼滿申請，但現時丁屋申請告示幾乎全面消失，意味沒有任何新申請。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，鄉議局就此情況，短期內將與地政總署開會，要求該署更改反對機制，據知討論內容包括將張貼告示期由14天縮短為7天、告示只張貼在普通市民無法進入的鄉事委員會、只由原居民反對丁屋申請、每宗申請只能反對一次等。<br />\n<br />\n記者上周四（14日）到元朗地政處10樓觀察，該處張貼小型申請屋苑申請的告示版，確已不見任何丁屋申請告示。<br />\n<br />\n就網民發起的丁屋申請行動有否影響申請數量，以及會否更改反對丁屋申請機制，地政總署均未有正面回覆，僅指由今年1月1日至8月31日，該署共接獲1,942宗小型屋宇申請個案，同期分別批出557宗及拒絕651宗申請，但該署並無備存反對申請的數字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190919/60058970?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60058970%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5X4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=85b6c583\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60058970%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=f911532a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190919/60058970?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a>"},{"pid":"584feab5d201ab7aeef359d9d4173458c754fe5e","tid":1580290,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"919 12點半UST Way，5點沙田聯校人鏈<br />\n920 1點半港大美國旗隊，5點荃灣中學人鏈<br />\n921 2點屯門再光復，7點元朗靜坐<br />\n922 12點沙田巡迴合唱團，和你suck4.0<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">929 全球反赤納粹</span></span>"},{"pid":"94c10132742ebcd44ccd994dbb6d2765b6b467fc","tid":1580290,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"嚇撚到班牛屎佬瀨屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f0539f48e7088b248f7374af92daa0e6ca293f","tid":1580290,"uid":34466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"地政肯撚定會跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432b65266e90bd5ec4a7faab1414ef822eedfe3a","tid":1580290,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦，收埋左貼在後巷ja"},{"pid":"d429907847dc83ca13e04232f364fa97132dc58e","tid":1580290,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:05:17.000Z","msg":"地政你咪跪呀"},{"pid":"01bae4fcc5a07556abcb779baf912da36984515e","tid":1580290,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驚就唔好申請</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d5a53dfaef2c9fa560693d899be7c750351c4df","tid":1580290,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"keep going"},{"pid":"7e92f7987543c8069b098b8af2c01722f114eb63","tid":1580290,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"繼續唔好停<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1c655aa8cd05349fb7d390d86bf20d78437b46","tid":1580290,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"消息人士指出，鄉議局就此情況，短期內將與地政總署開會，要求該署更改反對機制，據知討論內容包括將張貼告示期由14天縮短為7天、告示只張貼在普通市民無法進入的鄉事委員會、只由原居民反對丁屋申請、每宗申請只能反對一次等。"},{"pid":"e639648a71c268ee6b23abd2729b2550cbd4924f","tid":1580290,"uid":235458,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"機制對你不利就要逼人改到岩你心水 香港真係到處都充滿中國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57a9397fe4f79d4983ada0b58bb0049f936b985","tid":1580290,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"只可由原居民提出反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982585aeba6e390284ca9ec5ad4d3521f6a6bb72","tid":1580290,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnLxWAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnLxWAc.jpg&h=5ea06781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2Leqwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2Leqwm.jpg&h=6f74c0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期： 9月21日 時間：2:00集合，3點起步<br />\n路線：新和里  -&gt; 屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n屯門公園<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(一)禁打賞</span><br />\n 要求修改《遊樂場地規例》，禁止一切在公園範圍內涉及任何形式金錢之打賞，行乞，捐贈行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">(二)投訴權</span><br />\n 呼籲立法會民政事務委員會各委員正視民意，盡快修訂《遊樂場地規》使附近街坊同樣擁有投訴權利<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(三)加強執法</span><br />\n 要求康文署增加合資格執法人員及簡化檢控程序，加強執法及檢控違法行為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(四)正視設施不足</span><br />\n 要求康文署及屯門區議會，正視區內老人文娛設施不足問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">(五)檢討管理</span><br />\n 要求康文署檢討屯門公園及割下公共空間的管理，有效分配公園及其他公共空間的使用權<br />\n<br />\n交通：<br />\n巴士： <br />\n58M / 58X / 63X / 260X / 960 - 紅橋站落車<br />\n黨鐵：<br />\n1. 西鐵兆康站落車<br />\n2. 轉乘輕鐵 751 (往友愛）或610 （往屯門碼頭）"},{"pid":"cceee8e50557ba2f5426d890f31db31b29ccd6d0","tid":1580290,"uid":252960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"「要求更改反對機制，包括縮短張貼期、只可由原居民提出反對，以及每宗丁屋申請只可反對一次等。」<br />\non9到呢，只可由既得利益者反對既得利益者，真係膠都費時俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8147e201334d3bb9cab8244627ba610f2c50fde6","tid":1580290,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"[復仇閪] 國際級反套丁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579504</a><br />\n<br />\n做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fb95d5b689647656c6a81c1fca614b8314b509","tid":1580290,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"好後悔點解以前唔識玩俾佢地起咁多樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c0b79fbaadfe125757fd76d669e68d8ce52920","tid":1580290,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cceee8e50557ba2f5426d890f31db31b29ccd6d0","tid":1580290,"uid":252960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"「要求更改反對機制，包括縮短張貼期、只可由原居民提出反對，以及每宗丁屋申請只可反對一次等。」<br />\non9到呢，只可由既得利益者反對既得利益者，真係膠都費時俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"反對一次咪即係過硬？"},{"pid":"d0bde6b67c87f5fc004b483fafe36d84f256580b","tid":1580290,"uid":57151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3521430bca8694714cb4d91ad53c1916b69c8aca","tid":1580290,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7fb95d5b689647656c6a81c1fca614b8314b509","tid":1580290,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"好後悔點解以前唔識玩俾佢地起咁多樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"香港好多腐敗野，只係以前冇人理會。既然公眾唔理，政府就梗係唔會理。<br />\n宜家不論係popo執法，定係套丁都進入左大眾視野，其實係一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，遲d d 鄉黑會唔會日日搵人守住元朗地政架？見一獲打一獲"},{"pid":"fd624e10c33c3afbf920615ac53ba4c4ff0ea630","tid":1580290,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3521430bca8694714cb4d91ad53c1916b69c8aca","tid":1580290,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7fb95d5b689647656c6a81c1fca614b8314b509","tid":1580290,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"好後悔點解以前唔識玩俾佢地起咁多樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"香港好多腐敗野，只係以前冇人理會。既然公眾唔理，政府就梗係唔會理。<br />\n宜家不論係popo執法，定係套丁都進入左大眾視野，其實係一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，遲d d 鄉黑會唔會日日搵人守住元朗地政架？見一獲打一獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"真係正仆街黎，而家真香港人要扲返主導權！！"},{"pid":"a13f0ae1b75b2a4bf83bbb0c3a5779163c2e563d","tid":1580290,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"班牛屎佬企錯邊 <br />\n如果企起抗爭者個邊<br />\n仲有機會一國兩制 仲可能繼續有地<br />\n<br />\n可惜你打完香港人 <br />\n<br />\n香港人攬炒 一國一制 <br />\n之後第一時間開你刀"},{"pid":"010f979e